{"tid":2159732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【網民和你唱　警質疑多個網媒非註冊報刊】","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T13:38:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7085df4d6517db59e9648ac371d47500206de4","tid":2159732,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3364858916933038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3364858916933038&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=3fdc86cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3364858916933038</a><br />\n<br />\n【網民和你唱 警質疑多個網媒非註冊報刊】<br />\n<br />\n「和你 Lunch」常客 David 與朋友二人，今日傍晚參與網民發起的「香港人終極和你唱」，由國際金融中心 IFC 步行至中區警署，沿路喊「五大訴求，缺一不可」的口號。David 到達警署後警方拒絕他進內，並驅趕他及在場記者至警署對面的行人路，又拉起封鎖線，其間傳媒聯絡隊要求記者展示記者證，又質疑《香港獨立媒體網》、希望之聲、《SocREC 社會記錄頻道》等網媒記者的所屬傳媒機構非註冊報刊，將他們帶到一旁查核。<br />\n<br />\nDavid 被數名警員包圍並截查後獲放行，他事後引述警方指，假如再不離開會有大批警員「招呼」他，他隨後離開。他昨日參與梁凌杰悼念會期間被警方拘捕，凌晨 3 時保釋，他說警方以他違反「限聚令」將他拘捕。"},{"pid":"a8b045293cac7babf29afdff9c1bd02662e6c289","tid":2159732,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a13602a361efaaa2b6432e97bde41f2a9ae8a66","tid":2159732,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /